{"tid":2440313,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"西藏爆發武裝衝突 開啟達賴逃亡生涯","createTime":"2021-03-10T00:55:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T08:10:56.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5d044849b095a334eb6dd8c9857b74dce973c7a7","tid":2440313,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/NDIO0rVRjSkoK9bdI6bFOg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/57i0O4MWdlPlEj7a1AkSRw--~B/aD0zNjY7dz02NTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cts.com.tw/f548b0d03839e8b059e6ac2a63a39f7d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FNDIO0rVRjSkoK9bdI6bFOg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTM2MC4zNjkyMzA3NjkyMzA4%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F57i0O4MWdlPlEj7a1AkSRw--~B%2FaD0zNjY7dz02NTA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fcts.com.tw%2Ff548b0d03839e8b059e6ac2a63a39f7d&h=80323823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1959年3月10日，西藏人民與解放軍在拉薩發生武裝衝突，抗議從1950年中國軍隊進入後，採取的高壓統治。7天後，藏人不敵解放軍的鎮壓，原本領導西藏政府的第十四世達賴喇嘛開始了流亡生涯。此後3月10日被訂為西藏的人民起義日，每年舉辦紀念活動或是示威抗議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/歷史上的今天-西藏爆發武裝衝突-開啟達賴逃亡生涯-004200992.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9-%E8%A5%BF%E8%97%8F%E7%88%86%E7%99%BC%E6%AD%A6%E8%A3%9D%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81-%E9%96%8B%E5%95%9F%E9%81%94%E8%B3%B4%E9%80%83%E4%BA%A1%E7%94%9F%E6%B6%AF-004200992.html&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplfzvTpW%2BvScgizIMFshFG5Q%3D&h=437427ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/歷史上的今天-西藏爆發武裝衝突-開啟達賴逃亡生涯-004200992.html</a>"},{"pid":"8b0ada5bb48a9cefb94d458cf33d1851dc1bbffc","tid":2440313,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T01:04:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src